                               GET IN TOUCH


At the moment, your best bet would be to try calling some of the
following BBS...

The Edge Of Chaos	
Digital Chaos           (0141) 339-2776 (9pm > )
DockMaster              
Duck & Cover            
Magnum BBS              (01236) 452 724 (7pm > )


I have only printed the numbers of the BBS where the Sysop's have given
permission for me to do so. All of these BBS are fairly small, and the
Sysop's have said they would rather avoid taking on new users who only
want to come on to leave me mail. I take their point completely, and
so these numberless ones are only really open for existing users.

If you are going to call the above BBS, please PLEASE take note of the
TIME! They're not 24 hours!!!!!!

Oh, I can do "requests" if you like.. Just get in touch, telling me which
game you want hacked, and if I have it, I'll give it a go and release the
POKE as a guide file as well as attaching it to the reply (and if I'm
feeling generous, I'll give you a mention).

I'm trying to arrange some other way of letting you get in touch with me,
but I'm not going on the InterNet as I personally didn't like it that much
when I was on.. Certainly not enough to justify forking out the cash I was.
While I quite like the idea of getting feedback from people, I'm wary of
leaving my real address, as the last thing I want is calls from people who
have looked my name up in the phone book, as others who have done this have
lived to regret it, losing sleep (and causing family arguments) thanks to
crank calls at un-Godly hours. I hope you understand.

Anyway, I'll keep you all posted of any future developments that arise
(if any).

Rastan.
